194
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,560
I don't do portraits.

195
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,400
No portraits?

196
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:49,680
You...

197
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:52,120
But these non-portrait paintings look great.

198
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,720
Just draw one for us, please?

199
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,600
Look, it's my first day here.

200
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:57,600
If you like any of my existing works,

201
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:58,640
you can pick one.

202
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,560
Then we can discuss the price.

203
00:12:00,560 --> 00:12:02,360
But I really don't do portraits.

204
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:05,840
If you don't do portraits, why are you even on the street?

205
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,600
I...

206
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,640
You want portraits, right?

207
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:09,240
Yes.

208
00:12:10,560 --> 00:12:12,080
Over there. They do portraits over there.

209
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,080
You should go there instead.

210
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,120
We don't like that style.

211
00:12:14,120 --> 00:12:16,320
I think your paintings are really good.

212
00:12:17,560 --> 00:12:19,120
