234
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:14,610
So you're aspiring to be an artist?

235
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:16,660
Have you signed with any gallery?

236
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:17,760
No.

237
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,840
I want to open my own gallery.

238
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:21,240
That's quite ambitious.

239
00:13:21,480 --> 00:13:23,340
Do you understand the art market?

240
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:25,320
Not really.

241
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:30,370
