270
00:15:02,520 --> 00:15:05,780
don't scam people under the pretense of running a gallery.

271
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:07,000
So...

272
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,930
These paintings weren't even done by you.

273
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:14,680
Every single one of these paintings was done by me.

274
00:15:18,280 --> 00:15:19,610
My name is Jiang Xiaoyu.

275
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:21,720
Please have the actual artist

276
00:15:21,720 --> 00:15:23,080
contact me. Goodbye.

277
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:32,240
Jiang Xiaoyu

278
00:15:32,960 --> 00:15:34,680
Someone bought Mom's painting so quickly.

279
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:35,600
Mom is amazing.

280
00:15:35,680 --> 00:15:37,010
Come on, blow Mom a kiss.

281
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:39,680
Give me a break.

282
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:42,220
